Sorry. Uh...

272
00:11:39,095 --> 00:11:40,528
Better?

273
00:11:40,530 --> 00:11:41,696
Oh, baguettes.

274
00:11:41,698 --> 00:11:43,898
Yes, I like baguettes.

275
00:11:43,900 --> 00:11:46,100
What exactly
are you doing?

276
00:11:46,102 --> 00:11:48,536
Determining baseline fear levels
in capuchin monkeys

277
